  "texts": [
    "To identify tandem repeats enriched in pericentromeric and subtelomeric regions, we extracted the monomer sequences of all tandem repeats overlapping the region of interest.",
    "A database of non-redundant monomers was created by making a dimer database.",
    "Dimers were clustered with BlastClust 186 v2.2.26 (-S 75 -p F -L 0.45 -b F -W 10).",
    "A non-redundant monomer database was created using the most common monomer size from each cluster.",
    "The non-redundant sequences were mapped to the genome with BLASTN 187 (BLAST+ v2.9.0; -outfmt 6 -evalue 1e3)."
  ],
